  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mentally Aware Nigeria Initiative is proud to bring you Knot Undone: An Anthology of Mental Illness in Nigeria. Featuring seventeen stories that portray what it&apos;s like to live with a mental illness in Nigeria from the eyes of those that have lived out this grueling reality. In a country where mental health stigma is a culture, where do people that cope with these illnesses hide? In Shame or in denial? And right in front of our very eyes?  This will be the first collection out of the series.</narrative>
  </description>
